vantage of that sure as hell won't be comfortable... and hitting more than 4 at once in any zone is likely to cause the 5th to get jumbled/lost on the way to the PC.<br><br>Keyboard technology is still stuck in the 1980s. If someone knows of a board that can handle all the punishment I'm describing, for the love of god man please share that information, I've been looking for something like that forever.<br><br>You can tell I've thought about this far too much. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>On a side note, I despise the Windows keys. They interfere with proper gaming... <p><b>Raviel Darkfyre</b><BR><table style="filter:glow(color=Red, strength=3)"><font color="black" size=2><b>Insidious Blood</b></font></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uzikoz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zikoz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Disciple</span><br>  Posts: 424<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(8/1/02 6:54:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=142.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Changing Pet to &quot;Pulling&quot; window.</span><hr size=1> I was surprised to find that lots of people apparantly use the  left button for forward.  For me, left button is strictly used for targeting or hotkey selection (for me at least).  I was shocked a bit when people started complaining about the targeting bug. I went in and tried to duplicate it and no matter how many times I moved my mouse over someone, it didn't target them, even when i was right clicking. Heh. Until I came back and re-read the posts, I didn't realize it was because they were also using left click for forward.  To me, using the left mouse for forward negates the adva